Title: The different world
DateModified: '2019-03-11'
DatePublished: '2019-03-11'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-different-world
SetInCountry: Afghanistan
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Wahidullah Saberzai
AuthorCountry: Afghanistan
Text: 'For first time I have troveld to Europe country there is small country it name
  is Portugal. I spent my whole life in war zone country Afghanistan when i saw Portugal
  i realized how much the world is different Portugal was very beautiful, cleen I
  saw people who walking in the street thay have no tension of bomb blast but in Afghanistan
  we can walk in the street we afraid there will be bomb. There was peace, happiness.

  I saw different world'
